N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 1240.5 - Committee Counsel and Staff

State Regulations

Each Department of the Appellate Division
shall appoint to a Committee or Committees such chief attorneys and other staff
as it deems appropriate. Notes
